# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:9
translate portuguese dana0_4b30accf:

    # "I decide to go back inside the office and chat with Dana a little bit more. I turn off the car and walk back into the building."
    "Decido voltar para dentro do escritório e conversar um pouco mais com a Dana. Desligo o carro e volto a entrar no edifício."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:11
translate portuguese dana0_bfd0c735:

    # cw "Oh hey, did you forget something?"
    cw "Oh, olá, esqueceste-te de alguma coisa?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:12
translate portuguese dana0_003419c5:

    # pc "No, I just wanted to come in and chat for a bit."
    pc "Não, só queria entrar e conversar um bocadinho."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:14
translate portuguese dana0_928517bb:

    # cw "Oh, with me?"
    cw "Oh, comigo?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:15
translate portuguese dana0_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:17
translate portuguese dana0_cce31900:

    # "Dana's face grows a bit red."
    "O rosto da Dana fica um pouco vermelho."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:18
translate portuguese dana0_bb093f6c:

    # cw "Oh, well I'm kind of busy right now. I have to organize all this stuff before I can go home, and I have to be home at seven."
    cw "Oh, bem, estou um pouco ocupada agora. Tenho de organizar tudo isto antes de poder ir para casa, e tenho de estar em casa às sete."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:22
translate portuguese dana0_356ae111:

    # cw "You would do that? Sure, pull up a chair."
    cw "Fazes isso? Claro, puxa uma cadeira."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:26
translate portuguese dana0_8dbdc8d1:

    # cw "No problem. See you Monday."
    cw "Sem problema. Vemo-nos na segunda-feira."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:29
translate portuguese dana0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/dana_seeyoutomorrow.mp3"
    voice "voices/dana_seeyoutomorrow.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:30
translate portuguese dana0_9da3accd:

    # cw "No problem. See you tomorrow."
    cw "Sem problema. Vemo-nos amanhã."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:31
translate portuguese dana0_e8e6d974:

    # "I head back to the car and leave."
    "Volto para o carro e vou-me embora."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:36
translate portuguese dana0_b791cdf1:

    # "I take one of the chairs and pull it over next to her. I spend the next hour going through the stacks of paper on her desk and sorting them by date."
    "Pego numa das cadeiras e puxo-a para junto dela. Passo a hora seguinte a vasculhar as pilhas de papel na secretária dela e a organizá-las por data."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:37
translate portuguese dana0_34290a3e:

    # "It is easy work and Dana is good company. We don't talk much, but every time I catch her eye, she is smiling."
    "É um trabalho fácil e a Dana é boa companhia. Não falamos muito, mas sempre que cruzo o olhar com ela, ela está a sorrir."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:38
translate portuguese dana0_2dbc8990:

    # "We finish just before seven."
    "Terminamos pouco antes das sete."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:41
translate portuguese dana0_02cb5af0:

    # cw "Oh my God, thank you so much for helping me. There's no way I would've finished it in time if you weren't here."
    cw "Meu Deus, muito obrigada por me ajudares. Não havia hipótese de eu ter terminado a tempo se não estivesses aqui."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:42
translate portuguese dana0_a7c1d064:

    # pc "No problem. Glad to help."
    pc "Não há problema. Fico feliz por ajudar."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:43
translate portuguese dana0_3a92acde:

    # cw "You're the best. I have to run though, so I'll see you later, okay?"
    cw "És o máximo. Mas tenho de ir, por isso vemo-nos mais tarde, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:44
translate portuguese dana0_82f4d7ef:

    # "I don't really want to say goodbye to her, and I get a sudden burst of courage."
    "Não quero mesmo dizer-lhe adeus e sinto uma súbita onda de coragem."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:45
translate portuguese dana0_4005f1c2:

    # pc "I'm kind of hungry. Want to grab a bite to eat somewhere?"
    pc "Estou com um pouco de fome. Queres ir comer qualquer coisa a algum lado?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:47
translate portuguese dana0_a9645bb5:

    # "Her smile fades away a bit."
    "O sorriso dela desvanece-se um pouco."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:49
translate portuguese dana0_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/dana_sortofengaged.mp3"
    voice "voices/dana_sortofengaged.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:50
translate portuguese dana0_92e7ded7:

    # cw "I'm not sure that's a good idea. I'm sort of engaged. I don't think he'd like to see me talking to other guys outside of work."
    cw "Não sei se é boa ideia. Estou meio que noiva. Acho que ele não ia gostar de me ver a falar com outros rapazes fora do trabalho."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:51
translate portuguese dana0_1dad11d2:

    # pc "Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't mean to make you feel uncomfortable."
    pc "Oh, desculpa. Não queria que te sentisses desconfortável."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:53
translate portuguese dana0_094901ac:

    # voice dana_seeyoulater
    # cw "It's okay. I'll see you later, okay?"
    voice dana_seeyoulater
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:57
translate portuguese dana0_437e96ea:

    # "She smiles and guides me out the front door so that she can start closing up the office."
    "Ela sorri e acompanha-me até à porta da frente para poder começar a fechar o escritório."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:58
translate portuguese dana0_7679afbc:

    # "Struck out. Oops. Maybe I shouldn't have pushed it? Oh well."
    "Foi por água abaixo. Oops. Talvez não devesse ter insistido? Paciência."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:59
translate portuguese dana0_75b9bff6:

    # "I head back to the car."
    "Volto para o carro."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:1
    old "Dana needs some help with her paperwork after work."
    new "A Dana precisa de ajuda com a papelada depois do trabalho."

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:2
    old "You could help her any weekday evening after you finish work."
    new "Podes ajudá-la em qualquer noite da semana depois de terminares o trabalho."

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:20
    old "Maybe I could help you sort?"
    new "Talvez eu possa ajudar-te a organizar?"

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:23
    old "Oh, I'll leave you be then."
    new "Oh, então vou deixar-te em paz."

